## Cluster configurations

minikube start --cpus=5 --vm-driver hyperv --hyperv-virtual-switch "Primary Virtual Switch" --kubernetes-version=v1.16.10
minikube addons enable ingress


# Delete
kubectl delete -k .\tools\monitoring\
